    "description": "Are you a skilled Real Estate Agent looking for your next big career move? Indiabulls Real Estate in Tiruchirappalli offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Indiabulls Real Estate:\nIndiabulls Real Estate is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Source and close property deals with prospective buyers and investors\n• Coordinate with architects, contractors, and project teams\n• Build relationships with channel partners and brokers\n• Prepare presentations and proposals for institutional clients\n• Manage relationships with existing customers post-purchase\n• Conduct site visits and property presentations for clients\n• Conduct market research and provide competitive analysis\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Property Valuation\n• Proficiency in Investment Analysis\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n• Proficiency in GIS Tools\n• Proficiency in Contract Management\n• Proficiency in Due Diligence\n• Proficiency in Property Management\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Tiruchirappalli, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Indiabulls Real Estate!",
